            <title>[HBASE-1276] [testing] Upgrade to JUnit 4.x and use @BeforeClass annotations to optimize tests</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-1276</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If we upgrade to JUnit 4.x we can get access to @BeforeClass annotations... that allows us to start up DFS &amp;amp; Hbase only once per test class.  This should improve the speed of our unit tests substantially.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We will also need an ability to reset the hbase state between tests however.  Drop all tables for example.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
